query:
SELECT c.name as lemsa_name, COUNT(p.id) as protocol_count
FROM counties c
LEFT JOIN protocolChunks p ON c.id = p.countyId
WHERE c.state = 'California'
AND c.name IN (
  'Alameda County EMS Agency', 'Central California EMS Agency', 'Coastal Valleys EMS Agency',
  'Contra Costa County EMS', 'El Dorado County EMS Agency', 'Imperial County EMS Agency',
  'Inland Counties EMS Agency', 'Kern County EMS', 'Los Angeles County EMS Agency',
  'Marin County EMS', 'Merced County EMS Agency', 'Monterey County EMS Agency',
  'Mountain-Valley EMS Agency', 'Napa County EMS', 'North Coast EMS',
  'Northern California EMS Inc', 'Orange County EMS Agency', 'Riverside County EMS Agency',
  'Sacramento County EMS Agency', 'San Benito County EMS', 'San Diego County EMS',
  'San Francisco EMS Agency', 'San Joaquin County EMS Agency', 'San Luis Obispo County EMS Agency',
  'San Mateo County EMS Agency', 'Santa Barbara County EMS Agency', 'Santa Clara County EMS Agency',
  'Santa Cruz County EMS', 'Sierra-Sacramento Valley EMS Agency', 'Solano County EMS',
  'Stanislaus County EMS Agency', 'Ventura County EMS Agency', 'Yolo County EMS Agency'
)
GROUP BY c.id, c.name
ORDER BY protocol_count DESC;
